node.text:
Today myself and @minikai had a revelation about confidence. He wanted to shoot some hoops today, so we headed down to the courts. To his dismay, his skills did not match what he had envisioned in his mind. Thoughts of failure begun to sink in...

We’re not born with spectacular talents. They’re obtained over extended periods full of highs and lows. With failures comes mental challenges. When negative thoughts clouded with discouragement begin to creep in, we must be armed with the internal strength and confidence to push onward. Positive reinforcement is your driving force to forbid the thought of quitting from entering the mind. 

You don’t need to be the top dog in the game. You don’t need to make history. But you should always chase what brings you happiness in life. Your attitude is the obstacle standing between you and your dreams.  You are unique and you DO have the ability to achieve all you set your mind to!

node.text:
4%

What does it take to be more? To evolve into the next stage?

4% of your day. 60 minutes out of the 1440 in a day where you shut the world off. A blocked out time where you enter your own realm and the anxious spirit within you takes over. 60 minutes of the day where the outside forces are relinquished of power, and your sights are set on personal growth. 

Make the most of this time dedicated to working on yourself. Power through every workout with relentless force with @redcon1. Shop my supps through the link in my bio ✔️

#Redcon1 
#HighestStateOfReadiness

Fitness Evolved.

Old school strength with new school vibes. @vivafitnessgo sets the tone for you to dominate your training each and every day. With plate loaded strength machines to next gen technology heavy duty cardio pieces, this is your one stop shop for all your fitness needs.

Power up your training with VIVA Fitness. Check out the line through the link in my bio ✔️

#VIVAFitness
#PushYourself
